{
  "stem": "15694.8",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Whereas it was going abnormally slow the day before, it gathered such a speed, it went so fast, that I said to my father, this speed is mean-- meant to make it impossible to jump.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We know there's no more-- no more doubt now.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We have to escape, come what may.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I said, to confuse the guards, I jump on one side, you on the other.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We do the same time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I step on the head of the shoulder of the person opposite, and you on the head of the sho-- shoulder and head of this one to reach the wall and then we jump at the same time.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And to do that, I count two, and on the-- on your count of three, we'll jump.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Come with me, because Auschwitz is the end.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So my father said, OK.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But before we do that, he would take out every scrap of socks or what have you to put around your hand.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And everything else, dress to make the fall sort of easier.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The impact.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And that's what we did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And this day-- glorious summer's day, first of August-- we were looking like we were going to the North Pole.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the neighbor onto whose head my father was to step, got up, eyed us conspic-- suspiciously, and said, I was-- oh, by the way, I was counting one, two, I was ready for the tiger jump.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But the three never came because the neighbor had stood up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "My father also eyed the area and hoped for a patchy a-- you know, grass or something, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "A patch of grass, you know, to-- to ease the fall.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
